nk" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Y%C3%AAn-%C4%91%C3%A0i-thi-Thu/poem-dMgvUhW-sRBAQiAP5rPO9Q">Yên đài thi - Thu - 燕臺詩－秋</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
